Willem Frens (together with Rajat Bharadwaj) initiated the development of the EMBER Methane Pyrolysis technology development within TNO. This is a technology to produce hydrogen from hydrogen without CO2 emission. Additional advantages:
- Hydrogen production cost are similar to steam methane reforming;
- Hydrogen can be produced in high volumes;
- Solid carbon aand hydrogen is produced without CO2 emission.

